- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses graph temporal logic specifications. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control of multi-agent systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with spatial-temporal tasks and control of agents.
